<verse number="6" style="v" />May he come down like rain on the mown grass,</para>

<para style="q1">like showers that water the earth.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />May the righteous flourish in his days,</para>

<para style="q1">and may there be an abundance of peace till the moon is no more.</para>
